snippet.title: The Rewinder - Available Now with Xbox Game Pass - Accolades Trailer
snippet.description:
The Rewinder is now available on Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, Windows, and with Xbox Game Pass and PC Game Pass. 

The Rewinder is an adventure puzzle game based on Chinese mythology. You play as Yun, the last known Rewinder, who can communicate with spirits and explore other people's memories to alter the past.

https://www.xbox.com/games/store/the-rewinder/9pj2hr6wgrnd
